    "description": "The Dark Crown: Genesis is a 2d rogue-lite skill-based action platformer, where you can easily switch between abilities throughout the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150940/extras/1396a05a4a59983813739b338e1bb9fb.poster.avif?t=1729341937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150940/extras/1396a05a4a59983813739b338e1bb9fb.webm?t=1729341937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150940/extras/1396a05a4a59983813739b338e1bb9fb.mp4?t=1729341937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As one sacrificed for the kingdom, you'll steal the powers of the Demons and their cursed weapons to escape the hellish endless dungeon.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150940/extras/a664be9df1a6fea8c6394fbdf879aa24.poster.avif?t=1729341937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150940/extras/a664be9df1a6fea8c6394fbdf879aa24.webm?t=1729341937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150940/extras/a664be9df1a6fea8c6394fbdf879aa24.mp4?t=1729341937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><i>Warning: Some features listed below are not yet available in the current version and will be added.</i><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 5 Procedural levels - Explore levels with unique enemies and environments.<br></li><li> 50+ Relics - Vary your build with cursed relics.<br></li><li> 5 Weapon Types - Kill the demons with their own weapon.<br></li><li> 5 Bosses- Face 5 great demons, each with their own Dark element.<br></li><li> 5 Mini Bosses - Meet the 5 greatest generals of all time.<br></li><li> 5 Skills and 15 Skill Updates - Gain and master the demons' greatest powers.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150940/extras/6a2d5a1b0d83f290edcce3bb4a2966ce.poster.avif?t=1729341937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150940/extras/6a2d5a1b0d83f290edcce3bb4a2966ce.webm?t=1729341937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150940/extras/6a2d5a1b0d83f290edcce3bb4a2966ce.mp4?t=1729341937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
